&lt;p>Whether your patients are managing a chronic condition, recovering from an injury, or simply want peace of mind, &lt;strong>SH+™ wearable band&lt;/strong> is designed to bring clinical-grade insight to your patients wrist -without interrupting their lives.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="anchor">
