&lt;div class="anchor">
&lt;h3 id="-imu-inertia-measuring-unit" id="-imu-inertia-measuring-unit">🧭 IMU (Inertia Measuring Unit)&lt;/h3>
&lt;a class="" href="#-imu-inertia-measuring-unit" aria-label=": 🧭 IMU (Inertia Measuring Unit)">
 &lt;svg aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
