&lt;/a>
&lt;/div>
&lt;p>Track body movement, posture, and fall events with a high-precision IMU. From subtle shifts to sudden impacts, &lt;strong>SH+™ wearable band&lt;/strong> captures motion data in real time—useful for physical therapy monitoring, elderly care, and fall detection.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="anchor">
&lt;h3 id="-pulse-sensor" id="-pulse-sensor">💗 Pulse Sensor&lt;/h3>
&lt;a class="" href="#-pulse-sensor" aria-label=": 💗 Pulse Sensor">
 &lt;svg aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
