 &lt;path d="M14 10a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 -5 0l-4 4a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 5 5l.5 -.5" />
 &lt;/svg>
&lt;/a>
&lt;/div>
&lt;p>Local alerts ensure you (or the wearer) never miss a critical event. When thresholds are crossed—like abnormal heart rate or lack of movement—a discreet buzzer provides instant feedback, even before the cloud gets the message.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="anchor">
&lt;h3 id="-wi-fi-enabled-gateway-to-cloud-connectivity" id="-wi-fi-enabled-gateway-to-cloud-connectivity">📶 Wi-Fi Enabled: Gateway-to-Cloud Connectivity&lt;/h3>
&lt;a class="" href="#-wi-fi-enabled-gateway-to-cloud-connectivity" aria-label=": 📶 Wi-Fi Enabled: Gateway-to-Cloud Connectivity">
 &lt;svg aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
